pesticide.PPE: long-sleeved shirt and long pants; chemical-resistant gloves made of any waterproof material; shoes and socks
pesticide.signal_word: KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN

Safety_Information.general_Info: Harmful if inhaled or absorbed through the skin. Causes moderate eye irritation. Avoid breathing spray mist. Avoid contact with skin, eyes or clothing. Wash thoroughly with soap and water after handling and before eating, drinking, chewing gum, using tobacco, or using the toilet.
